sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as Database/PVC<br/>JDBC/File TLS1.2+

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 1: External TrustyAI API Access

    Client->>Route: HTTPS Request<br/>Auth: None (transport only)
    Route->>OAuth: Forward Request<br/>TLS 1.2+ Re-encrypt
    OAuth->>OAuth: Validate OAuth Bearer Token
    OAuth->>TrustyAI: HTTP Request<br/>Validated OAuth
    TrustyAI->>DB: Store/Retrieve Data<br/>JDBC or File I/O
    DB-->>TrustyAI: Data Response
    TrustyAI-->>OAuth: API Response
    OAuth-->>Route: HTTPS Response
    Route-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 2: Model Inference Monitoring

    participant InfClient as Inference Client
    participant KServe as KServe InferenceService<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh<br/>mTLS
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>80/TCP HTTP

    InfClient->>KServe: Inference Request<br/>Bearer Token
    KServe->>ModelMesh: Process Inference
    ModelMesh->>TrustyAI: Send Payload Data<br/>443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    TrustyAI->>DB: Store Inference Metrics<br/>JDBC/File
    DB-->>TrustyAI: Stored
    TrustyAI-->>ModelMesh: ACK
    ModelMesh-->>KServe: Inference Result
    KServe-->>InfClient: Prediction Response

    Prometheus->>TrustyAI: Scrape /q/metrics<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    TrustyAI-->>Prometheus: Metrics (fairness, explainability)

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 3: LMEvalJob Execution

    participant Operator as TrustyAI Operator
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Driver as LMEval Driver<br/>Init Container
    participant LMEval as LMEval Pod<br/>Batch Job
    participant HF as Hugging Face Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LMPVC as PVC Storage

    Operator->>K8s: Create LMEvalJob Pod<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>Driver: Start Init Container
    Driver->>LMEval: Initialize Job<br/>Shared Volume
    LMEval->>HF: Download Models/Datasets<br/>API Token (optional)
    HF-->>LMEval: Model Files
    LMEval->>LMEval: Execute Evaluation
    LMEval->>LMPVC: Write Results<br/>File I/O
    LMPVC-->>Driver: Results Available
    Driver->>Operator: Job Status Update<br/>Pod Exec
    Operator->>K8s: Update LMEvalJob Status
